# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

##	[1.0.0] - 2024-08-26

###	Added
- Initial public release of the `@su-labs/notifications` library.

- Introduction of `SuNotificationService` for managing notifications with reactive `Signals`.

- Introduction of `SuNotificationComponent`, a standalone component for rendering notifications.

- Support for multiple notification types: `info`, `success`, `warning`, `error`, and `custom`.

- Highly configurable options for message, duration, auto-close, custom CSS classes, and icons.

- Support for default SVG icons, inline SVG strings, or image URLs.

- Multiple screen positions supported: `top-right`, `top-left`, `bottom-right`, `bottom-left`, `top-center`, and `bottom-center`.